window.bookSummaryJSON = "In <i>Snow Crash</i>, Neal Stephenson took science fiction to dazzling new levels. Now, in <i>The Diamond Age</i>, he delivers another stunning tale. Set in 21st-century Shanghai, it is the story of what happens when a state-of-the-art interactive device falls into the hands of a street urchin named Nell. Her life, and the entire future of humanity, is about to be decoded and reprogrammed."; 
